<lb n="0478b12" ed="T"/>名秋大仙。太白大仙名歲大仙。無<note n="0478009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔諍〕－【元】【明】</note><note n="0478009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諍【大】，〔－〕【元】【明】</note><app n="0478009"><lem wit="【大】">諍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大仙諍
