<lb n="0478b14" ed="T"/>一角大仙。<note n="0478010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仙角＝仙覺【宋】【元】，名覺【明】</note><note n="0478010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仙角【大】，仙覺【宋】【元】，名覺【明】</note><app n="0478010"><lem wit="【大】">仙角</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">仙覺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">名覺</rdg></app>大仙揭瞿大仙。單茶耶那大
