<lb n="0478b16" ed="T"/>仙赤馬大仙毛聚大仙無樂大仙。<note n="0478011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（名仙）＋吉【三】</note><note n="0478011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吉【大】，名仙吉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0478011"><lem wit="【大】">吉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">名仙吉</rdg></app>膩盧大
