<lb n="0478b19" ed="T"/>以此大孔雀王呪經。擁護某甲令<note n="0478012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝壽【三】</note><note n="0478012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，壽【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0478012"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">壽</rdg></app>百歲得
